LET'S TRY A SCREWBALL !

01:21:24.747 --> 01:21:28.884
- TURN, TURN, TURN !
- BE COOL ! OW !

01:21:28.918 --> 01:21:32.521
HEY ! HO !
COME ON, BOY !

01:21:32.555 --> 01:21:34.423
SCREWBALL ! BOOM !

01:21:34.457 --> 01:21:36.559
WHOA ! OOOH !

01:21:36.592 --> 01:21:40.629
