Tires Screeching ]

01:23:29.605 --> 01:23:34.410
WHOA ! OH ! OH !
KID ! KID !

01:23:34.443 --> 01:23:37.846
WHAT ARE YOU DOIN' ?
OH ! OH !

01:23:37.880 --> 01:23:41.684
KID, KID, STOP,
PLEASE, PLEASE ! STOP !

01:23:41.717 --> 01:23:44.653
OH !
[ Groaning ]

01:23:44.687 --> 01:23:47.423
KID, PLEASE !
DON'T DO THAT !

01:23:52.861 --> 01:23:56.932
OOOOH !
[ Screaming ]

01:24:07.610 --> 01:24:10.546
