YOU'RE NOT A VERY
NICE BOY, YOU KNOW THAT ?

01:24:21.957 --> 01:24:24.460
FREEZE !
PRESTON, ARE YOU OKAY ?

01:24:24.493 --> 01:24:27.696
WHAT'S THIS ALL ABOUT ?
WHAT'S HAPPENING HERE ?

01:24:27.730 --> 01:24:31.134
