WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE ?

01:24:31.167 --> 01:24:34.403
LET GO !
AS OF THIS MOMENT,
YOU'RE FIRED FROM MY BANK !

01:24:34.437 --> 01:24:37.573
F.B.I., BIDERMAN.
FROM THIS MOMENT,
YOU'RE FIRED FROM YOUR BANK.

01:24:37.606 --> 01:24:40.743
