- YOU'RE WITH THE F.B.I. ?

01:24:40.776 --> 01:24:46.149
YES, PRESTON, I AM.
OKAY, KID, FINALLY, AT
LONG LAST, WHO'S MACINTOSH ?

01:24:46.182 --> 01:24:50.486
UH, UH, UH, UH,

01:24:50.519 --> 01:24:52.621
UH, UH,

01:24:52.655 --> 01:24:54.923
UH, UH--

01:24:54.957 --> 01:24:57.660
