- YOU'RE MACINTOSH ?

01:24:57.693 --> 01:25:00.663
I'M MACINTOSH !
AND I WANT YOU ALL
OFF MY PROPERTY NOW !

01:25:00.696 --> 01:25:03.499
HE'S MACINTOSH.
YOU SURE ?

01:25:03.532 --> 01:25:06.135
I TELL YA, I'M MACINTOSH !
