WE SAY THE PARTY NEEDED ?
ICE CREAM, RIGHT ?

01:27:33.949 --> 01:27:37.553
I JUST WENT TO GET ICE CREAM.
I DON'T KNOW IF I GOT
THE EXACT RECIPE,

01:27:37.586 --> 01:27:40.389
